        <h3>Importance of hydration in basketball</h3>

        <p>Hydration is very important, changes usually occur during intense sports practice
            in body weight, caused mainly by loss of water in the form of sweat and breathing.
            <br />
            <br />
        The two hours before the game you should drink fluids to compensate for any subsequent losses.
            It is also important to drink during the game distributed every 20-30 min.
            It is convenient to take advantage of the time you remain on the bench to replace fluids.
